  "body": "Mixins make things unclear. For example:\n\n``` javascript\nReact.createClass({\n   mixins: [A, B, C, D],\n\n   anEvent: function() {\n      this.foo()\n   },\n\n   // ...\n})\n```\n\nIt will be hard for people to find out from which mixin does the `foo` come. They may have to search for the 4 mixins' documentation to know it. If the `anEvent` is hard to trigger, they even cannot use the devtool to trace the source code of `foo`.\n",
